query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `rag_chunks` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `documentId` int NOT NULL,
  `content` text NOT NULL,
  `chunkIndex` int NOT NULL,
  `embedding` text NOT NULL,
  `previousChunkSummary` text,
  `nextChunkSummary` text,
  `tokenCount` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `startChar` int NOT NULL,
  `endChar` int NOT NULL,
  `sectionTitle` varchar(255),
  `sectionLevel` int,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `rag_chunks_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  INDEX `rag_chunks_document_id_idx` (`documentId`),
  INDEX `rag_chunks_chunk_index_idx` (`documentId`, `chunkIndex`)
);
